24:55.000 --> 24:57.360
sing
like Luther Vandross, nigga?

24:58.880 --> 25:00.980
[Bryant]
Trust me when I say...

25:01.180 --> 25:03.200
I'm gonna wipe that
fuckin' smile off your face.

25:03.400 --> 25:05.200
You can't, 'cause then I'm just
gonna send my condolences

25:05.400 --> 25:07.140
to little Kevin.

25:07.340 --> 25:08.770
[Terry]
<i>And we got a police scanner,</i>

25:08.970 --> 25:10.820
in case you got stupid
and called for backup.

25:11.020 --> 25:12.210
[Meech] Yeah, you know, you
violated my fucking family

25:12.410 --> 25:13.730
for so long,

25:13.930 --> 25:16.190
it's about time
I fucking demonstrate.

25:16.390 --> 25:19.120
♪ ♪

25:27.820 --> 25:30.520
[footsteps approaching]

25:37.440 --> 25:39.150
I found a preacher.

25:39.350 --> 25:41.870
<i>Seemed decent, honorable.</i>

25:42.070 --> 25:44.320
